Package com.alcatel_lucent.nz.wnmsextract.reader

Reader package contains Reader classes designed to read an assortment of filetypes and Extractor classes that dismantle archive files into readable files.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
HttpReader Reader for http requests but defining date ranges.
LogWriter Interface defining call to logRawTableChanges, a method intended to write to a trigger aggregation table

ExtractorTNZCPV Deprecated.
ExtractorTNZTAR Deprecated.
FileSelector FileSelector's purpose is to pull/unzip extract data from a defined source and leave copies of the reqd xml files in a common directory
FileUtilities Deprecated.
GTAHttpReader GTA extension of fileselector.
SSLReaderUtilities Utility class that sets up a fake/empty security certificate so SSL clients don't get stressed when they dont have a matching certificate (because it hasn't been provided) and quit.
